#

Crispy Potato Pancakes

35 min
$8.5
350 kcal
Difficulty: 30%
Servings: 4

Allergens:

EggsGluten (optional)

Dietary Tags:

VegetarianGluten-Free Option

Cuisine:

American

Course:

Main Dish

Tags:

BreakfastComfort FoodEasy

Description

Deliciously crispy and golden brown potato pancakes, perfect for breakfast or a light meal!

Ingredients

  • russet potatoes: 4 large
  • eggs: 2
  • all-purpose flour: 1/2 cup
  • green onions: 1/4 cup, chopped
  • salt: 1 teaspoon
  • black pepper: 1/2 teaspoon
  • vegetable oil: 1/4 cup
  • sour cream: for serving
  • applesauce: for serving
